description: This Chainlink VRF common Chukcha purrs with a rating of 57, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 114, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, 1 for East, Box for South, and 1 for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/30572-11411-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Chukcha [114 Votes, Common]
